title: Health Care Practitioner Maternal Mental Health Continuing Education Requirements
subject: regulation of professions and occupations

abstracts.abstract: Health Care Practitioner Maternal Mental Health Continuing Education Requirements;  Providing curriculum requirements relating to maternal mental health for the required continuing education hours for licensure renewal; requiring a board, or the Department of Health if there is no board, to periodically update specified curriculum and accept the successful completion of such curriculum as credit toward continuing education requirements, etc.
